@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ebglwi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v0 * v1)
    v2 = (tmp + (wp.sin(v0 + 0.34) + wp.abs(tmp + 0.77)))
    tmp = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.26 - tmp + 0.28)) / v0)
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.55)) * wp.sin(wp.sin(v2 + 0.57)))
    tmp = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.36 / v2 + 0.83) * wp.sin(v1 + 0.02)))
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.abs((tmp + 0.54 + tmp + 0.35)))
    data[tid] = v0
